<span style="color: #ff0000;">It's the poison of Negativity.</span>
<ol>
 	<li>If someone put poison in your water, would you drink it? The obvious answer is ‚Äòno‚Äô! Chemical poisons that we can see, taste, touch and smell can be fatal. Fortunately, we are intelligent enough to know that we do not ingest ourselves with poisonous substances.</li>
 	<li>Similarly, we have to remove out negativity harmful to our <strong>MIND</strong>¬†.¬†Negativity is the poison that prevents us from achieving our dreams. Hence we need to stop it before it contaminates our lives.</li>
